menu2.murder.name: Murderer
menu2.murder.desc: The murderer wins when everyone else is dead.
menu2.murder.desc2: He can throw his knife by right-clicking while holding the knife.
menu2.murdertp.name: §aTeleporter (Murder.Inc) §2[murderer power]
menu2.murdertp.desc: The murderer can use this remote to teleport
menu2.murdertp.desc2: himself at the location he is looking at!
menu2.murdertp.desc3: This item can only be used 4 times in a game.
menu2.detective.name: Detective
menu2.detective.desc: The detective's goal is to kill the murderer
menu2.detective.desc2: If he kills a bystander, he will drop his gun.
menu2.players.name: Bystanders
menu2.players.desc: Bystanders have to survive until the murderer
menu2.players.desc2: is killed or police has arrived.
menu2.players.desc3: Some of them can have a special ability.
menu2.players.desc4: Bystanders can also gather gold ingots to
menu2.players.desc5: get a gun for 15 gold ingots.
menu2.ghost.name: §aGhost §2[Bystander ability]
menu2.ghost.desc: The ghost can make himself invisible,
menu2.ghost.desc2: to escape or pickup the gun.
menu2.drugged.name: §aDrug addict §2[Bystander ability]
menu2.drugged.desc: The drug addict can take a sting of adrenalin
menu2.drugged.desc2: to get a temporary speed boost.
menu2.taser.name: §aTaser §2[Bystander ability]
menu2.taser.desc3: Use it wisely since it's a single use item.
menu2.angel.name: §aAngel §2[Bystander ability]
menu2.angel.desc: The player who killed the angel is
menu2.angel.desc3: You can't discover who is the murder
menu2.angel.desc4: through walls but you have the position.
menu2.terrorist.name: §aSuicidal §2[Bystander ability]
menu2.terrorist.desc: When the suicidal dies, he triggers his explosives
menu2.terrorist.desc2: that kills everyone in a 4 blocks radius.
menu2.terrorist.desc3: A little mark uppon head of the suicidal
menu2.terrorist.desc4: warns the murder about the danger.
menu2.terrorist.desc5: The murder has to deal with the explosion or
menu2.terrorist.desc6: kill the suicidal at the end of the game.
menu2.lighter.name: §aLighter
menu2.lighter.desc: Set people on fire and slow them down.
menu2.lighter.desc2: Watch out, if you cross his trail you will catch fire.
menu2.shield.name: §aShield
menu2.shield.desc: Become invicible for a short period of time
menu2.gun.name: §aDesert Eagle
menu2.tp.name: §aRandom teleporter
menu2.tp.desc: Teleports you to a random location on the map.
menu2.trap.name: §aTrap
menu2.trap.desc: Set an invisible trap that will stun
